race.comment: ALZARO (11) resumes having shown good ability in two city runs last time in, second on debut at Moonee Valley before an even effort at Caulfield. Comes back a fair way in grade now and should take beating. ROMANTIC MISS (12) is coming along nicely, close up in two runs back from a spell this time in. Better for them and can improve to 1100m third up. SIRLEAF (4) has been thereabouts in two runs back from a spell and should be ready to fire from the good draw. I'M HELRO (7) is a Deep Field mare on debut who can run well. Has trialled on several occasions so far this year, winning most of them including two so far this prep.
